channel.title: TweezyScape!
channel.description:
Hey guys im making a bran new server from SCRATH! I used defaultscapes v2 for base, so far ive added new home, new starter gear, npc's, got some doors to open, cleared out some space and about to transfer my npc's into a better training area (if i figure how 2 add npc's LOL) When the server is finished im gona make a client for it aswell ^^
download microsoft word document, dunno hw 2 post pics LOL
